    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2011 Porsche Cayman S (987.2), a definitive mid-engine driver\u2019s car featuring the robust 3.4L DFI flat-six engine. This powerplant eliminates IMS concerns and provides immediate throttle response across the rev range. The 6-speed manual transaxle offers short, mechanical throws, paired with a factory-optioned limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis is enhanced with PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management), maintaining excellent damping characteristics. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive borescope inspection, new ignition coils, and a fresh brake fluid flush for the four-piston monobloc calipers. While the front fascia shows minor road rash consistent with enthusiast mileage, the mechanical synchronization and lateral grip remain uncompromising. This is an honest, driver-focused example with a clean DME overrev report.",
